description.about:
Welcome to the game "Mahjong Kitchen".
Mahjong Kitchen is a variation of the classic Chinese symbol matching puzzle game.
Unlike classic mahjong, the game offers additional mechanics for world-famous mahjong:
with each new level the number of icons increases - to infinity (!), so the goal of the game becomes to achieve the highest possible level;
the game takes place for a limited time;
the size and shape of the playing field adapts to the size of your screen;
Leaderboards help you evaluate how successful you are in the game!
